<li><a href="http://www.burtoniana.org/books/1884-Camoens%20the%20Lyricks/index.htm" class="external text" title="http://www.burtoniana.org/books/1884-Camoens%20the%20Lyricks/index.htm" rel="nofollow"><i>Camoens. The Lyricks</i> 2 Vols (1884)</a></li>
