<li><cite style="font-style:normal" class="book" id="CITEREFLovell1998"><a href="/wiki/Mary_S._Lovell" title="Mary S. Lovell">Lovell, Mary S.</a> (1998). <i>A Rage to Live: A Biography of Richard &amp; Isabel Burton</i>. New York: <a href="/wiki/W._W._Norton_%26_Company" title="W. W. Norton &amp; Company">W. W. Norton &amp; Company</a>.</cite><span class="Z3988" title="ctx_ver=Z39.88-2004&amp;rft_val_fmt=info%3Aofi%2Ffmt%3Akev%3Amtx%3Abook&amp;rft.genre=book&amp;rft.btitle=A+Rage+to+Live%3A+A+Biography+of+Richard+%26+Isabel+Burton&amp;rft.aulast=Lovell&amp;rft.aufirst=Mary+S.&amp;rft.au=Lovell%2C+Mary+S.&amp;rft.date=1998&amp;rft.place=New+York&amp;rft.pub=%5B%5BW.+W.+Norton+%26+Company%5D%5D&amp;rfr_id=info:sid/en.wikipedia.org:Richard_Francis_Burton"><span style="display: none;">&#160;</span></span></li>
